{
  "stem": "22582.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always find the-- the holidays, I guess Sukkot was very nice holiday, happy holidays, usually.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I never liked to be too much in-- in-- in synagogue praying all day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the less I had to go to pray, the better I felt, I guess.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always with the family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always in our house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- my sister was married when I was 12.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she was always coming with-- then she had a family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She used to come to-- to our house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my brothers were not home, as far as I remember later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because one-- one was in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one was in France.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And but we used to visit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father had-- had some brothers and sisters in town, so used to visit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they used to come.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had family from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They used to come also, sometimes for the holidays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that's [INAUDIBLE] many, the family-- the very close family that we have.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- no, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I remember my father's grandmother-- my father's mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember her when she was already in bed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were always telling-- they were telling stories how smart she was when she was-- she was not sick, that she was a business woman.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was running the-- the stores.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And but at that time she was-- they called it-- I don't know whether it was Alzheimer's.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she was in the 60s.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she was considered in 60s very old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember she was always in bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were saying that she had [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That means the artery closed up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and she died when she was in the 60s.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't remember, my grandfather, my father's father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was dead when I was born.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
